Classes

BlackjackEngine
This is the game engine that manages the deck and coordinates player bets/decisions.

Player
Object representing a player who has a bankroll, can take multiple seats at a table, and will make game decisions when prompted.

Shuffler
The shuffler keeps track of the shoe and deals/shuffles cards upon the game engine's request.

Counter
Any object that implements the counter interface can subscribe to all card updates from the game engine to keep track of the count.

Todo
Maybe use additional interfaces to support different game types (double down, free bet, 22 is push for dealer)